I3D Ass1 Sample Solution written by Jesse Archer

To compile on linux type:
make

If you want to compile with optimisation flags, add the flag:
opt=y

If you want co compile with debugging enable, add the flag:
dbg=y

ie:

make opt=y dbg=y



To compile on windows, use the vcxproj file provided with Visual Studio 2010 express edition


The program expects the files boat.obj and boat.mtl to be in the same folder


Use arrow keys to control the boat as well as the following keys:

Esc/q : quit
w : toggle wireframe mode
n : toggle normal visualisation
a : toggle axis rendering
l : toggle light between day/night
